features: 😼【Industrial Style Shelves】Our large bookshelf maximize the vertical storage and display space, industrial style design, and perfect integration of classic and fashion. With polished brown MDF borax, black metal style finish and open design, it looks elegant and luxurious.It will add a delicate atmosphere to your space. Whether it is placed in the living room, bedroom or office, it will also add sparkle to your life.

😼【High Quality Materials & Sturdy Frame】The double bookshelf is made of high-quality metal and selected panels. It adopts the top rust proof coating. The combination of firm metal material and gentle wood gives a grace and modest temperament. With the thick panel and heavy metal frame with X-shaped frame backing, the stability of the bookshelf is enhanced. This bookshelf is sturdy and stable, each board can hold up to 70 lbs and protect your items perfectly.

😼【More Storage & Display Space】 This 6-Tier double row bookshelf has 10 open shelves, which provides very large storage space. It not only meets the storage needs of daily life, but also can place your decorations on this large display shelf freely. The bookshelf panel is waterproof and scratch resistant, which is very easy to clean. Give away 4 detachable hooks.Oversize: 47.24''W x 11.8 '' D x 72.44''H.

😼【Multi-function Use】This 6 tier bookshelf can be used as bookshelf for bedroom， shelves for living room, office shelves, bathroom cabinets, and storage organizers in kitchens, balconies, corridors or any other space. The design of the bookshelf is very suitable for matching with other furniture.
😼【Easy Installation & After-sales Service 】The bookshelf is attached with clear and detailed instructions, and each part is carefully labeled. We provide tools for assembly.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Big and Sturdy Shelf
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. This shelf is great! It took me about about an hour to assemble solo and the instructions were VERY clear. Everything went together seamlessly and the only issue I had was putting things in backwards a couple of times, but it was easy to fix.The drawers close so smooth and everything feels very sturdy. It is rustic and beautiful and I can't wait to fill it up with books and plants.It feels like I got a very expensive shelf without having to pay for a very expensive shelf.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 16, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Just what we were looking for!
reviews.reviewText: I searched for a very long time for a shelf for our boardgames that also had drawers to keep our nosy puppy out of our game accessories, lol. And this one fit the vision perfectly. Could not be happier with how it turned out. It looks great in our living room and is just the right size for the space & our needs. It took like four hours to assemble, but we are pretty inept at building, lol. If you're more competent than we are, it should probably only take an hour or two to do. Directions were pretty clear, concise, & easy to follow.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars I HAVE ONLY ONE COMPLAINT
reviews.reviewText: 1. I LOVE IT.2. Whoever designed this got it slightly wrong in all ways for building.--the shelves all bow up at the center because the length of the vertical pieces is slightly off.--I had a damaged foot screw and no extras. I had to hammer it after I placed it, so good luck ever taking it off.--the back brace pieces are just on the side of too short to be attached by the screws, which led me to stripping a screw (I had ONE extra) and not being able to get two screws in all the way. Also they're gold while everything else is black or silver. Annoying.--the instructions are VAGUE. I read them and examined them before I started and still managed to do and redo the same piece 4x until I was mad. For your reference, the shelves should have the hangover lip in the center while the edges should be flush when put together. Screw the edges in on both sides before you do the center with the brackets. Save yourself a headache.--the fancy x in the center of the shelf will look great, but good luck screwing in your pieces. There's everything in the way, and it is annoying to do mini half turns over and over again. It can be done.--I appreciated the clear labeling of every piece!--I did have to anchor the shelf for stability, and the pieces were provided for that.It is a gorgeous piece, it holds everything I want and has edge hooks!! I can hang my bag and jacket on the side to grab on my way out or keys, umbrella, head band, winter gear, whatever. I didn't know that feature was on the shelf, so it was a good added surprise at the end.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great Company, Great shelf!
reviews.reviewText: Absolutely love this shelf! I tried to put it together myself, which was a big mistake. It says two people for a reason, and as soon as my son helped, it was quick and easy to assemble. My first shelf came with a very small error in manufacturing, but the company took care of it right away, and I was able to get a whole new shelf. Amazing experience! Great customer service! Everything about this was just wonderful, and I look forward to filling my shelf with more joyful items.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 3, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I wasn't able to upload a photo of the finished product unfortunately. I was hesitant to purchase because it only had a few reviews. It took a few hours for 2 of us to assemble but it wasn't difficult at all. Once it was finished and assembled, I absolutely love it! It's very sturdy. I left out a few shelves because I used it for my plants and some were too tall to fit. If you're on the fence, I would say buy it and you won't be disappointed. It's a very lovely piece. It looks exactly like the picture. I'm glad I bought it.
